    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Distinct portions, sections, or divisions of a surface, especially when sunk below or raised above the general level or enclosed by a frame or border. Common on walls, ceilings, and doors, and also on furniture pieces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
